wg93(dataframe)からindicator行列をつくりそれにCAを行う

#mjca(wg93[,1:4],lambda="indicator") %>% str()
#wg93[,1:4] %>% caconv(from="rpm",to="ind") -> wg93.ind # これは、CとDがすべて0！bug？
wg93[,1:4] %>% GDAtools::dichotom() -> wg93.ind
res.CA <- CA(wg93.ind,graph=FALSE)

Exhibit 20.1

fviz_ca_biplot(res.CA,map="rowprincipal",invisible = "row",label = "col",title = "Exhibit20.1") + coord_fixed(ratio = 1)

rlin <- res.CA2$row$coord[,1:2]
p <- plot(res.CA,graph.type = "ggplot")
p <- p + geom_line(aes(rlin[1:7,1],rlin[1:7,2]),colour="green",linetype = 2) + 
  geom_point(aes(rlin[1:7,1],rlin[1:7,2]),colour="green")
p <- p + geom_line(aes(rlin[8:14,1],rlin[8:14,2]),colour="pink",linetype = 3) + 
  geom_point(aes(rlin[8:14,1],rlin[8:14,2]),colour="pink")
p
res.CA$eig[1:2,1]
##     dim 1     dim 2 
## 0.4573792 0.4309658
res.CA$col$coord[,1:2] -> rlin0 # coord は標準座標
rlin0 / sqrt(res.CA$eig[1:2,1]) -> rlin # ルート（固有値）で割って主座標に変換
fviz_ca_biplot(res.CA,map="rowprincipal",invisible = "row",label = "col",title = "Exhibit20.1 破線追記") + coord_fixed(ratio = 1) -> p
p <- p + geom_line(aes(rlin[1:5,1],rlin[1:5,2]),colour="black",linetype = "dashed")  
p <- p + geom_line(aes(rlin[6:10,1],rlin[6:10,2]),colour="blue",linetype = "dashed")  
p <- p + geom_line(aes(rlin[11:15,1],rlin[11:15,2]),colour="green",linetype = "dashed")  
p <- p + geom_line(aes(rlin[16:20,1],rlin[16:20,2]),colour="red",linetype = "dashed",size=1)  
p
